data.title: Scams - trailers, cars, motorcycles, dirt bikes, laptops
data.description:
These are all scams trying to get your contact info. Often they require you to respond with a phone number. 
Sometimes they respond telling you the listing is on another website. 
If it seems too good to be true, it probably is.
